00:36:57.240 --> 00:36:58.320
There are certain
people on my team

00:36:58.320 --> 00:37:00.360
who need a meeting with
me every single week.

00:37:00.360 --> 00:37:01.380
There are certain
people on my team

00:37:01.380 --> 00:37:02.850
who need to talk
to me every day.

00:37:02.850 --> 00:37:05.160
There's other people on my
team who do really well, who

00:37:05.160 --> 00:37:07.980
I have to go after for updates.

00:37:07.980 --> 00:37:09.810
And that's just sort
of the way they work,

00:37:09.810 --> 00:37:13.080
and so I'm not a big fan of
creating rules and then making

00:37:13.080 --> 00:37:14.490
team members stick by them.

00:37:14.490 --> 00:37:16.620
I want people to be
able to move flexibly,

00:37:16.620 --> 00:37:19.410
to be as successful as
they possibly can be.

00:37:19.410 --> 00:37:22.470
And then they just have
to set those expectations

00:37:22.470 --> 00:37:23.430
for themselves.

00:37:23.430 --> 00:37:26.940
So at the end of the year,
I'll have a goal meeting.

00:37:26.940 --> 00:37:29.034
And my goal meeting, I
don't create numbers.

00:37:29.034 --> 00:37:30.450
I have them tell
me how much money

00:37:30.450 --> 00:37:31.890
they want to make next year.

00:37:31.890 --> 00:37:33.390
And they have to
make the number.

00:37:33.390 --> 00:37:34.590
It's not me.

00:37:34.590 --> 00:37:37.270
If they say, like, $5,
we have to move it up.

00:37:37.270 --> 00:37:39.259
But they have to set
the number, and then we

00:37:39.259 --> 00:37:41.550
back into that how much they
have to sell to get there.

00:37:41.550 --> 00:37:43.080
That's now their base salary.

00:37:43.080 --> 00:37:45.240
Everything else they
sell above that is bonus.

00:37:45.240 --> 00:37:46.920
If they sell under
the number they just

00:37:46.920 --> 00:37:49.680
said they want to sell, and
they don't come talk to me

00:37:49.680 --> 00:37:52.310
by June or July, saying,
"Listen, the year is terrible.

00:37:52.310 --> 00:37:54.935
New York City real estate market
has fallen through the floor,"

00:37:54.935 --> 00:37:57.420
something like that, then
they can't be with me.

00:37:57.420 --> 00:38:00.540
But I talk to my team more than
I talk to any other client.

00:38:00.540 --> 00:38:04.410
And I really view teams
as, like, football teams.

00:38:04.410 --> 00:38:06.570
I'm awful at every
sport known to man,

00:38:06.570 --> 00:38:08.970
but I do know how
football teams work.

00:38:08.970 --> 00:38:10.890
And it's important
that everyone can

00:38:10.890 --> 00:38:12.810
be their own
individual rock star

00:38:12.810 --> 00:38:15.780
and be successful and be
great at what they do.

00:38:15.780 --> 00:38:17.700
But you're not all going
to win, unless you're

00:38:17.700 --> 00:38:20.190
able to play well together
and work together and talk

