crazy or not, I always just--

00:43:27.070 --> 00:43:29.180
I wanted to be successful.

00:43:29.180 --> 00:43:33.350
I wanted to squeeze as much out
of life as possible, because I

00:43:33.350 --> 00:43:36.920
